data.description:
Located in a family-friendly neighborhood, this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is nestled in the sought out after Wylie ISD (West). The home offers an open living concept with engineered hard wood floors in the living room, crown molding and a wood burning fireplace that adds not only charm but warmth to the area.The kitchen comes equipped with stainless steel appliances including a gas range and double ovens, dishwasher and microwave. The spacious guest bedrooms offer ample space for your needs and large walk in closets. The guest bath provides granite countertops, dual sinks, and extra storage. The primary suite has a built in office area in the bedroom and in the bathroom the features include, a jetted tub, tiled shower, dual sinks
Outside, a well-maintained yard provides the ideal backdrop for outdoor gatherings, gardening, and family fun. Extra details include an extended patio, storage building, rain gutters and an extended driveway to the backyard.
